+### Question 3
+
+Use only semaphores. The idea is:
+
+- keep the number of free whiteboards in `freeBoards`,
+- place each arriving group into a FIFO waiting queue,
+- when boards are returned, admit as many waiting groups from the **front of the queue** as possible.
+
+This guarantees fairness (hence no starvation), avoids deadlock, and still allows multiple groups to be in the room at the same time.
